Install the docker: https://docs.docker.com/desktop/setup/install/windows-install
Create docker container:  docker-compose up -d --build
To rebuild container with updates: docker-compose up -d --build
Database user: sqladmin
Database password: sqladmin
Database name: expenses
Docker logs: docker-compose logs -f app
Export database DDL: docker-compose exec -T db pg_dump -U sqladmin expenses > my_backup.sql
Import database DDL: Get-Content my_backup.sql | docker-compose exec -T db psql -U sqladmin expenses
